    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>About Super Hyper, ULTRA!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Super Hyper, ULTRA! is a VR roguelite arcade shooter where you step into the shoes of a space mercenary willing to do whatever it takes to get rich.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight hordes of monsters across diverse environments as you travel from planet to planet. Slay thousands of enemies, level up, and experiment with loot to craft devastating combos, and become the terror of the system.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Think you’re up for the challenge? Prove you have what it takes to join the Super Hyper, ULTRA! team.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3202470/extras/f02b15fec6dcdcf8a123ed0827a2bd2a.poster.avif?t=1771347171\" width=1002 height=310 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3202470/extras/f02b15fec6dcdcf8a123ed0827a2bd2a.webm?t=1771347171\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3202470/extras/f02b15fec6dcdcf8a123ed0827a2bd2a.mp4?t=1771347171\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Endlessly replayable</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With over 70 unlockable items, every run is a new experiment.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Supercharge your health, unleash bizarre bullet effects, equip side guns, or throw bananas just to see what happens.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3202470/extras/43086d7ef23d854ea7d4da3e7e64c4cf.poster.avif?t=1771347171\" width=1002 height=310 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3202470/extras/43086d7ef23d854ea7d4da3e7e64c4cf.webm?t=1771347171\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3202470/extras/43086d7ef23d854ea7d4da3e7e64c4cf.mp4?t=1771347171\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Between planetary trips, stock up on insanely powerful, but outrageously expensive, items that can make your weapon unstoppable… or hilariously uncontrollable.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3202470/extras/210304edbabff30aaf619f49ceb859dd.poster.avif?t=1771347171\" width=1002 height=310 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3202470/extras/210304edbabff30aaf619f49ceb859dd.webm?t=1771347171\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3202470/extras/210304edbabff30aaf619f49ceb859dd.mp4?t=1771347171\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every playable character brings a unique playstyle, and you decide your planetary route, shaping every run exactly how you want it.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3202470/extras/34fc5759eaf8904981b0ea2414a2e69a.poster.avif?t=1771347171\" width=1002 height=310 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3202470/extras/34fc5759eaf8904981b0ea2414a2e69a.webm?t=1771347171\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3202470/extras/34fc5759eaf8904981b0ea2414a2e69a.mp4?t=1771347171\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Beat challenges to unlock run modifiers that twist the rules, making your runs tougher, weirder… and way more rewarding.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3202470/extras/93e10d5d2f86a66e92097ffcaf348fd3.webp?t=1771347171\" width=40 height=40 /></span> Full roguelite customization with 70+ items and upgrades for a variety of synergies and combos </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3202470/extras/ec973f5ec7e800b97802448a91597ddf.webp?t=1771347171\" width=40 height=40 /></span> Endless chaos with 200+ monsters coming at you</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3202470/extras/74cc2badebe8818fff2941eb415b690e.webp?t=1771347171\" width=40 height=40 /></span> Full and infinite replayability </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3202470/extras/5b762cbc05298e0ed7571b6ca1dd5b39.webp?t=1771347171\" width=40 height=40 /></span> Playable alone or up to 4 player</p></li></ul>",
